<https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/cities> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:topConceptOf <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:notation "1" ;
    dcterms:identifier "cities" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Cities (or Densely populated areas)"@en , 
        "Città o Zone densamente popolate"@it ;
    skos:definition "'Cities (or Densely populated areas)' — small spatial units that have at least 50 % of their population in 'Urban centres - High-density clusters'"@en , 
        "'Città o Zone densamente popolate': se almeno il 50% della popolazione ricade in uno o più 'Agglomerati ad alta densità (Urban centre)'"@it ;
    skos:related <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/urban-centres> .

<https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/towns-and-semi-dense-areas> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:topConceptOf <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:notation "2" ;
    dcterms:identifier "towns-and-semi-dense-areas" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Towns and semi-dense areas (or Intermediate density areas)"@en , 
        "Piccole città e sobborghi o Zone a densità intermedia di popolazione"@it ;
    skos:definition "'Towns and semi-dense areas (or Intermediate density areas)' — small spatial units that have less than 50 % of their population in urban centres and no more than 50 % of their population in 'Rural grid cells - Mostly low-density cells''"@en , 
        "'Piccole città e sobborghi o Zone a densità intermedia di popolazione': se meno del 50% della popolazione ricade in 'Agglomerati ad alta densità (Urban centre)' ma almeno il 50% della popolazione ricade in 'Agglomerati urbani (Urban cluster)'"@it ;
    skos:related <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/urban-clusters> .

<https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/rural-areas> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:topConceptOf <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:notation "3" ;
    dcterms:identifier "rural-areas" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Rural areas (or Thinly populated areas)"@en , 
        "Zone rurali o Zone scarsamente popolate"@it ;
    skos:definition "'Rural areas (or Thinly populated areas)' — small spatial units that have more than 50 % of their population in 'Rural grid cells - Mostly low-density cells'"@en , 
        "'Zone rurali o Zone scarsamente popolate': se più del 50% della popolazione vive in 'Celle rurali della griglia'"@it ;
    skos:related <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/rural-grid-cells> .

<https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/not-classified> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:notation "0" ;
    dcterms:identifier "not-classified" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Not Classified"@en , 
        "Non Classificato"@it ;
    skos:definition "Unclassified local spatial unit or cluster of contiguous cells"@en , 
        "Unità spaziale locale o aggregato di celle contigue non classificati"@it .

<https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/urban-centres> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:topConceptOf <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    #skos:notation "11" ;
    dcterms:identifier "urban-centres" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Urban centres - High-density clusters"@en , 
        "Agglomerati ad alta densità (Urban centre)"@it ;
    skos:definition """An urban centre (high-density cluster) — cluster of contiguous grid cells of 1 km² (using four-point contiguity, in other words, excluding diagonals) with a population density of at least 1 500 inhabitants per km²
        and collectively a minimum population of 50 000 inhabitants before gap-filling; if needed, cells that are at least
        50 % built-up may be added"""@en , 
        "Agglomerato ad alta densità (Urban centre): aggregato di celle della griglia regolare Geostat (griglia a maglia regolare - 1km, 10km, 100km - a fini statistici che ricopre l'intero territorio europeo, contenente la popolazione residente al censimento della popolazione e la percentuale di superfice ricoperta da acqua in ciascuna cella), contigue secondo i soli punti cardinali (4), dove ciascuna cella ha una densità di almeno 1.500 abitanti per km2 e, nell'aggregato, presentano almeno 50mila abitanti prima del riempimento delle 'lacune'."@it ;
    skos:related <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/cities> .

<https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/urban-clusters> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:topConceptOf <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    #skos:notation "22" ;
    dcterms:identifier "urban-clusters" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Urban clusters - Moderate density clusters"@en , 
        "Agglomerati urbani (Urban cluster)"@it ;
    skos:definition """An urban cluster (moderate-density cluster) — a cluster of contiguous grid cells of 1 km² (using eight-point
contiguity, in other words, including diagonals) with a population density of at least 300 inhabitants per km²
and a minimum population of 5 000 inhabitants. In a final step, the grid cells identified as an urban centre are
removed from the urban cluster."""@en , 
        "Agglomerato urbano (Urban cluster): aggregato di celle contigue, (anche per le sole diagonali, per un totale di 8 celle vicine), ciascuna con una densità di almeno 300 abitanti per km2 e che, nell'aggregato, hanno almeno 5mila abitanti."@it ;
    skos:related <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/towns-and-semi-dense-areas> .

<https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/rural-grid-cells> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    skos:topConceptOf <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies> ;
    #skos:notation "33" ;
    dcterms:identifier "rural-grid-cells" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Rural grid cells - Mostly low-density cells"@en , 
        "Celle rurali della griglia"@it ;
    skos:definition """Rural grid cells (or mostly low-density cells) — grid cells that are not identified as urban centres or as urban
clusters."""@en , 
        "'Celle rurali della griglia': celle della griglia regolare Geostat (griglia a maglia regolare - 1km, 10km, 100km - a fini statistici che ricopre l'intero territorio europeo, contenente la popolazione residente al censimento della popolazione e la percentuale di superfice ricoperta da acqua in ciascuna cella) da 1 km2 che non rientrano negli 'Agglomerati ad alta densità' o negli 'Agglomerati urbani'."@it ;
    skos:related <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/degurba/typologies/rural-areas> .               

